242
00:15:20,614 --> 00:15:23,950
Kenapa menemuinya?
Kenapa kau bertemu dengannya?

243
00:15:24,534 --> 00:15:27,120
Jong-ryeol, aku Jessica.

244
00:15:27,204 --> 00:15:30,499
