245
00:15:31,083 --> 00:15:32,918
Aku Jessica, Nyonya Kang Jong-ryeol.

246
00:15:34,336 --> 00:15:35,879
Pencari perhatian

247
00:15:37,005 --> 00:15:39,132
yang tak punya harga diri selain angkuh.

248
00:15:42,969 --> 00:15:44,012
Apa kau

249
