260
00:16:16,920 --> 00:16:18,839
Bom busuk sepertiku lebih berbahaya.

261
00:16:24,052 --> 00:16:25,303
Jangan pergi seperti ini.

262
00:16:25,387 --> 00:16:27,055
Sang-mi... Hei!

263
00:16:28,056 --> 00:16:29,099
Hei!

264
00:16:30,976 --> 00:16:32,310
Sial!

265
00:16:33,228 --> 00:16:34,146
Sialan.

