00:17:53,642 --> 00:17:56,353
Kau merasa takkan melihatku lagi?

279
00:17:56,853 --> 00:17:57,729
Kutaruh di sini.

280
00:17:59,481 --> 00:18:01,399
Entahlah. Perutku hanya sakit.

281
00:18:04,611 --> 00:18:08,406
Di masa lalu,
