286
00:18:22,045 --> 00:18:23,964
Lalu kenapa?

287
00:18:24,547 --> 00:18:25,465
Apa maumu?

288
00:18:26,967 --> 00:18:29,469
Awasi dia baik-baik. Paham?

289
