416
00:29:21,634 --> 00:29:25,930
Saling menjaga sungguh hal luar biasa.

417
00:29:28,141 --> 00:29:30,309
Jangan terlalu terharu dahulu.

418
00:29:30,393 --> 00:29:31,936
Aku bahkan belum mulai.

419
00:29:35,481 --> 00:29:38,234
Tak heran orang bisa tetap kuat
secara fisik dan mental.

420
00:29:38,317 --> 00:29:40,069
Ini alasannya.

421
00:29:42,864 --> 00:29:43,865
Dongbaek.

422
00:29:46,909 --> 00:29:48,202
Begini,

423
00:29:49,245 --> 00:29:50,079
aku tak tahu

424
